<project>
  <name>NEXUS — Personal Base of Operations</name>
  <description>
    Tauri v2 + React 19 desktop app combining network recon, dev environment management,
    encrypted credential storage, and AI-powered knowledge base.
    UI/UX: THE DIVISION 2 tactical HUD aesthetic.
  </description>
  <stack>
    <frontend>React 19 + TypeScript 5 + Vite 7 + Tailwind CSS 4 + Zustand 5</frontend>
    <backend>Rust + Tauri v2</backend>
    <testing>Vitest 4 (TS) + cargo test (Rust)</testing>
    <linting>Biome (TS/JS/JSON) + cargo clippy (Rust)</linting>
  </stack>
  <current_phase>Phase 1 — Foundation (完了) → Phase 2: RECON ウィング実装中</current_phase>
</project>

<design_system>
  <aesthetic>THE DIVISION 2 — タクティカルHUD、ミリタリーグリッド、機械的データパネル</aesthetic>
  <color_palette>
    CSS変数（src/index.css に定義済み）を必ず使うこと:
    - Background:  var(--color-base-950/900/800/700)
    - Accent:      var(--color-accent-500) = #f97316 (orange)
    - Highlight:   var(--color-cyan-500)   = #06b6d4 (cyan)
    - Danger:      var(--color-danger-500) = #ef4444
    - Success:     var(--color-success-500) = #22c55e
    - Text:        var(--color-text-primary/secondary/muted)
    - Border:      var(--color-border-subtle/active)
  </color_palette>
  <typography>
    - データ・コード・ラベル: var(--font-mono)
    - 一般テキスト: var(--font-sans)
  </typography>
  <components>
    - パネルには bracket-tl / bracket-br クラスでタクティカルコーナー装飾
    - 数値更新時は data-flash クラスを一時付与してフラッシュエフェクト
    - ステータスランプ: ● 文字 + success/danger/muted カラー
    - ローディング: animate-pulse スケルトン（Tailwind）
    - エラー: ページ上部バナー（danger 背景 rgba）
  </components>
</design_system>

<wing_architecture>
  <wing id="recon" phase="2">
    LAN network scanning, device monitoring, traffic visualization
    Commands: recon::scan_network, recon::get_traffic_snapshot
    Store: src/stores/useReconStore.ts
    UI: src/components/recon/ReconWing.tsx
  </wing>
  <wing id="ops" phase="3">
    Process management, Docker control, AI performance suggestions
    Commands: ops::list_processes, ops::get_ai_suggestions
    Store: src/stores/useOpsStore.ts
    UI: src/components/ops/OpsWing.tsx
  </wing>
  <wing id="vault" phase="4">
    AES-256 local credential storage, password/API key management
    Commands: vault::list_vault_entries, vault::unlock_vault
    Store: src/stores/useVaultStore.ts
    UI: src/components/vault/VaultWing.tsx
  </wing>
  <wing id="archive" phase="5">
    Markdown notes, graph visualization, Ollama semantic search
    Commands: archive::list_notes, archive::save_note
    Store: src/stores/useArchiveStore.ts
    UI: src/components/archive/ArchiveWing.tsx
  </wing>
</wing_architecture>

